<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>{{subject}}</title>
    {{> styles}}
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        {{> header}}

        <div class="content">
            <div class="notice-header">Notice to Attorney</div>

            <p class="greeting">Hi {{attorneyName}},</p>

            <p>
                <strong>{{tenantName}}</strong>'s 3-Day Notice has expired. Please see attached tenant's lease and all
                amendments (if any), 3-Day Notice sent to tenant, and tenant's accounting statement.
            </p>

            <div
                style="background-color: #f8fafc; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0; padding: 20px; border-radius: 6px; margin: 20px 0;">
                <p
                    style="font-weight: bold; border-bottom: 1px solid #e2e8f0; padding-bottom: 8px; margin-bottom: 12px; color: #1e293b;">
                    Contacts for tenant:
                </p>
                <p style="margin: 0; line-height: 1.8;">
                    <strong>{{tenantFullName}}</strong><br>
                    {{tenantCompanyName}}<br>
                    {{tenantAddress}}<br>
                    <a href="mailto:{{tenantMail}}"
                        style="color: #3b82f6; text-decoration: none;">{{tenantMail}}</a><br>
                    {{tenantContact}}
                </p>
            </div>

            <p>Please let me know if you need anything further to issue a demand.</p>

            <div class="closing">
                <p>Thanks,</p>
                <p>
                    <strong>{{userName}}</strong><br>
                    {{userTitle}}<br>
                    Global Fund Investments
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>

        {{> footer}}
    </div>
</body>

</html>